jUIRTE

A really simple (and light) Rich Text Editor (wysiwyg) for Jquery UI

== Featuring: ==
* Themeroller support
* Buttons & Buttonsets
* Expandable
* Cross-browser
* Light weight (and fast loading)

== Demo ==
* http://juichat.com/juirte/

== Example == 
 $(document).ready(function(){ 
  $("textarea").juirte();
 });

